node.text:
Eat your carbs! Just consider your source. 
✨
@wildgrainbox you get to enjoy your bread and pasta! One of my favorite things is their bread and rolls are slow fermented. Y'all know how much I love my fermented foods! 
✨
I think it's really important to not restrict what we feed ourselves but to be conscientious of the source. Make sure that the ingredients are clean and simple. And at wild green box it gives you the opportunity to eat your bread and pasta guilt free. 
✨
I want as many people as possible to enjoy the good stuff that you've been running from. For the first 50 people to sign up: $30 off the first box + FREE Brioche Rolls in every box! Use code THEONLYVEEBEE 
✨
Can't wait hear what y'all think! 
✨
#gmofree #fermented #cleaningridients #breadandbutter #pasta #brioche

node.text:
During cold/flu season Be pro-active & care for your immune system.
⭐️
Ginger juice (Costco has a big bottle rn for only $10 stock up or any grocer like Kroger, Ralph's or specialty store will carry the juiced ginger. 
Cayenne and cinnamon a dash of each. 
Make a 3 oz shot. Lemon helps with the intensity of the ginger. 
⭐️
Kombucha take with a potent clean blend or supplement of vitamin B&C with one drop of clove and a spruce oil. My personal preference is the Idaho Blue spruce. 
⭐️
4000 IU of vitamin D a day if taking daily, unless directed otherwise.  Your body only absorbs so much and the rest your liver holds onto which can lead to feeling nauseous. 
⭐️
If you don't like the smell of consuming raw garlic get the kryolic garlic caps take every single day. If you have sulfur sensitivity talk to your Doc about what another comparable option may be. 
⭐️
⭐️
⭐️
Doing this daily in combination with an anti inflammatory/gut healthy diet you'll be able to achieve a great level of wellness. Now if your eating fast food and sugary sweets all day I can't say how well this regime will help. 💪🏻

node.title: Your health is the one thing you 100% control over

node.text: Happy Birthday! I love you so much. I'm so grateful for you. Wishing you the greatest bday month ever! You deserve the most! You've been there for me in ways I never imagined a sister/friend ever could. You have my heart in the palm Of your hand for ever and always! My nana would have loved you. I know she's  looking down with so much joy knowing I have some one like you in my life. You were an acquaintance, then friend then best friend and now your my baby sis! God just dropped you off in my life and was like this what my 2 girls need. They need each other! And each other is what we got for life time after life time!

node.text:
Targeting the CNS (central nervous system) first and foremost has allowed the intensity that comes along with a sensory overload triggered by the physical discomfort of being sick to be more manageable. 
✨
Alkaline mineral soak with ginger. - baking soda and any sort of raw minerals. Try and stay away from commercial epson salts. 
✨
@simply.leaves lemon you out tea has ingredients that work directly with CNS as well as a gentle and safe detox. #sensoryissues #autism #holistichealth

node.text:
Starting your day upon waking in an alkaline/high frequency state is one of the many things I do to achieve overall wellness. 
💚
💚
Spirulina and chlorella (sea algae) mixed with Kombucha ( fermented tea) and 1 drop of spruce oil (pine tree family) is how I love to start my day. It aids in healthy detoxification. It’s purifying. It’s provides an environment to fight off illnesses. It allows for quicker recovery time and truly just adds to the longevity of your life! The combination of all of this is of such a high frequency that your body doesn’t know how to get sick and not be well!!!

Eat your carbs! Just consider your source. 
✨
@wildgrainbox you get to enjoy your bread and pasta! One of my favorite things is their bread and rolls are slow fermented. Y'all know how much I love my fermented foods!

I think it's really important to not restrict what we feed ourselves but to be conscientious of the source. Make sure that the ingredients are clean and simple. And at wild green box it gives you the opportunity to eat your bread and pasta guilt free. 
✨
I want as many people as possible to enjoy the good stuff that you've been running from. For the first 50 people to sign up: $30 off the first box + FREE Brioche Rolls in every box! Use code THEONLYVEEBEE 
✨
Can't wait hear what y'all think! 
✨

node.text:
During cold/flu season Be pro-active & care for your immune system.
⭐️
Ginger juice (Costco has a big bottle rn for only $10 stock up or any grocer like Kroger, Ralph's or specialty store will carry the juiced ginger. 
Cayenne and cinnamon a dash of each. 
Make a 3 oz shot. Lemon helps with the intensity of the ginger. 
⭐️
Kombucha take with a potent clean blend or supplement of vitamin B&C with one drop of clove and a spruce oil. My personal preference is the Idaho Blue spruce. 
⭐️
4000 IU of vitamin D a day if taking daily, unless directed otherwise.  Your body only absorbs so much and the rest your liver holds onto which can lead to feeling nauseous. 
⭐️
If you don't like the smell of consuming raw garlic get the kryolic garlic caps take every single day. If you have sulfur sensitivity talk to your Doc about what another comparable option may be. 
⭐️
⭐️
⭐️
Doing this daily in combination with an anti inflammatory/gut healthy diet you'll be able to achieve a great level of wellness. Now if your eating fast food and sugary sweets all day I can't say how well this regime will help. 💪🏻
